name: Cafe Lilliput

reviews.review_text: Cafe Lilliput is a vibrant seaside spot in Anjuna, Goa, with stunning ocean views and a laid-back vibe. The food is delicious, offering a mix of Goan and international cuisines. The atmosphere is perfect for both daytime relaxation and lively nightlife, featuring great music and beach parties. However, service during peak hours can be slow. Overall, it's a great place to unwind and enjoy the beach. Highly recommended for party lovers and ocean enthusiasts!

This is a wonderful place. We arrived there for lunch and spent good 6hrs. Had fish of the day, well prepared in Goan style , we ordered a lot of food and all of them were good. Beer, good food, beach and music. Awesome. BTW, some may feel service is slow but food is made to order and this place is for relaxing and enjoying the beqch.

liliput is a must-visit place if you are in North Goa and want to enjoy the best sea view, best cocktails and amazing food.
The view was just mesmerising.
Cocktails had many options to choose from.
In food, golden fried prawns and even calamari was excellent. loved their great portion size,
so this will be my fix spot in anjuna for sure.

description:
### Café Lilliput: A Seaside Retreat in Anjuna

Nestled along the stunning coastline of Anjuna, Goa, Café Lilliput boasts an inviting 3.9-star rating from an impressive pool of 8,863 reviews. This vibrant beach shack is a popular destination that resonates well with both locals and tourists, especially noted for its picturesque sunset views and laid-back ambiance. With tags such as "beach" (610 mentions), "ambience" (142), "sunset" (106), and "shack" (101), it’s clear that this restaurant captures the essence of coastal dining.

### Ambiance & Design

Upon entering Café Lilliput, guests are enveloped by a blissful atmosphere characterized by rustic beach aesthetics that perfectly complement the surroundings. The décor embodies a casual chic vibe, with colorful seating and beach-themed elements that create a welcoming environment. The interplay of natural light through the open structure enhances the overall experience, while the gentle sounds of the waves provide a soothing backdrop. Customers have highlighted the potential for lively beach parties, underscoring the dual nature of the locale as an ideal spot for both relaxation and excitement.

![Café Lilliput's Seaside View](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmpZ0LMabun8vKouOPE93_DYO5_AJjevnvL_h015mrZtwhzkxLFtfwZItIcOW23UiHd06Oydv_BcW_JKv28b5patn4SUBerXSHKyQFVO_H_yljoJ_a7a6bLL3NIENZbZQKskFJR=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Café Lilliput is famed for its blend of Goan and international cuisines, offering a diverse menu that caters to various palates. Highly recommended dishes include the "fish of the day"—an exquisite preparation that captures the fresh local flavors—and golden fried prawns that garner rave reviews for their perfect frying. Diners frequently mention the generous portion sizes, particularly praising the calamari as a delectable option. Furthermore, the cocktail selection has impressed guests, making it a go-to destination for refreshing drinks while enjoying the sea breeze.

![Delicious Goan Cuisine](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdm87aE2Lz2iFxvG8ht0gwK0p7e5_Y9dni31aNqeGAYdtJdQRp-cgLGcmKPt3Ys0aIhtANVN9HH1dAVjjXkUyMDCJ0gEFLkr4HnCZeOyNzpbZDalxzN7FAs3abySNf1WOFgUH3O9DQ=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

While the culinary delights and stunning views captivate guests, reviews have pointed out a few shortcomings regarding service—particularly during peak hours. Many patrons note that while the food is made to order, the wait times can be longer than expected. Nevertheless, the atmosphere is considered conducive to relaxation, allowing diners to unwind with a drink as they wait for their meals to arrive. Overall, staff friendliness seems to shine through, accentuating the welcoming nature of the restaurant.

### Popularity & Reviews

Café Lilliput has carved out a niche as a must-visit spot in North Goa for its breathtaking ocean views, diverse menu, and vibrant cocktails. The restaurant benefits from a robust online buzz, with myriad customers sharing their positive experiences across social media platforms. This popularity is further amplified by word-of-mouth recommendations from thrilled diners who describe it as a “fixed spot” for future visits.

![Relaxing Beachside Atmosphere](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlSLXyjvdXi2UNZoF7Xq2ZvGbtUEZf0wafPsf4vIqAyIOasxVAAdpOEs8xkh4fd00ic-vLaeXGI_FEHvh6XNmBGYDSWN4ztj6-Q6OxQrWUicm2opHfJBVxhiaKOIrF1Zrpnj6DNNA=w375-h563-p)

### Conclusion

Café Lilliput is more than just a restaurant; it’s a vibrant beachside haven that encapsulates the beauty and charm of Anjuna’s seaside life. With its combination of scrumptious food, refreshing drinks, and an inviting atmosphere, it’s perfect for those looking to unwind or party by the ocean. A blend of relaxation and energy, this eatery promises an experience that lingers long after the last bite is savored. Whether you’re a solo traveler, a couple, or a group of friends, Café Lilliput is well worth the visit for an unforgettable seaside experience.
